reviewText: I've appreciated Edie since the Sopranos. She presents a believable contemporarysaint of the wreck we call modern  health care. Just being around hospitals givesme the willies but I would be comforted to have somebody like Jackie; even withher addiction weakness. Very intelligently written and well acted series. Anenthusiastic thumbs-up for Nurse Jackie.
